#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn11.15"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn11.15:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 11 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 11 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn11.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn11.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Rāmaṇeyyakasutta "
msgstr "15. Delightful "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn11.15:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ jetavane. "
msgstr "Near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn11.15:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho sakko devānamindo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho sakko devānamindo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "And then Sakka, lord of gods, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side, and said to him, "

msgctxt "sn11.15:1.3"
msgid "“kiṃ nu kho, bhante, bhūmirāmaṇeyyakan”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, what is a delightful place?” "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.233, pts2ed1.500, sc2
msgctxt "sn11.15:2.1"
msgid "“Ārāmacetyā vanacetyā, "
msgstr "“Shrines in parks and forests, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.15:2.2"
msgid "pokkharañño sunimmitā; "
msgstr "well-made lotus ponds, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.15:2.3"
msgid "Manussarāmaṇeyyassa, "
msgstr "are not worth a sixteenth part "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.15:2.4"
msgid "kalaṃ nāgghanti soḷasiṃ. "
msgstr "of a delightful human being. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn11.15:3.1"
msgid "Gāme vā yadi vāraññe, "
msgstr "Whether in village or wilderness, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.15:3.2"
msgid "Ninne vā yadi vā thale; "
msgstr "in a valley or the uplands, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.15:3.3"
msgid "Yattha arahanto viharanti, "
msgstr "wherever the perfected ones live "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.15:3.4"
msgid "Taṃ bhūmirāmaṇeyyakan”ti. "
msgstr "is a delightful place.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
